00:22.256 --> 00:23.324
* WE SEE YOU, SCOOBY-DOO *

00:23.391 --> 00:25.193
* WE'RE COMING AFTER YOU *

00:25.259 --> 00:28.596
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

00:29.997 --> 00:31.432
* COME ON BACK *

00:31.499 --> 00:35.236
* YOU MAY FIND
ANOTHER CLUE *

00:35.303 --> 00:39.940
* SCOOBY SNAX WILL
BE WAITING HERE FOR YOU *

00:40.007 --> 00:41.242
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

00:41.309 --> 00:42.643
* WE'RE COMING AFTER YOU *

00:42.710 --> 00:45.879
* WE'RE GONNA SOLVE
